rComments: Just simply amazing. Super funny, engaging lectures, and doesn't play any tricks. Straight to the point and easy exams/quizzes. One of the best uOttawa profs.
C’est comme assister à un spectacle de Martin Matt ! Le prof est très drôle et très intéressant.
One of my favourite professors by far in my 3 years spent at university. He's very entertaining and manages to make every lecture and lab interesting. He's clearly passionate about what he teaches.

By far one of my favourite profs, his lectures were super interesting and he's super knowledgeable. The readings were necessary for the tests but they were always fair and not too heavy. I cannot say enough good things about this prof, I always looked forward to his classes and will be actively looking to take any of his other classes.

C'était mon cours préféré à l'uni. Il est super drôle et passionné par ce qu'il enseigne alors ses cours passent super vite. Les quiz sont faciles si tu écoutes bien en classe. Les examens sont sur la matière qu'il passe le plus de temps à expliquer. C'est quasi impossible de ne pas avoir A+.
He is an amazing prof. He makes everything clear. Go to class and you'll pass. I will definitely look out for more classes with him!

10/10!! I'm personally not a big fan of developmental psy but he made classes so much more fun & enjoyable!! Plus he's absolutely HILARIOUS!! I would recommend you to take this class (& prof Bureau in particular) if you can.

Overall a really good prof. Hes really funny you can tell he really knows and cares about what he teaches. He uses really good examples to make the material easier to understand. The quizzes, midterm and final are really easy. I do recommend this prof to anyone.
Best prof I've had by far. His lectures are so dynamic and he gives really good exemples to help understand. Would take a class again with him any day.

Jean-François is an amazing psych prof! Guy is hilarious, always cracking jokes and telling stories to better understand the course material. Overall an easy class, as long as you show up, listen and take some notes and read the textbook, you'll pass! Definitely recommend him and the course!
Prof Bureau is amazing. he is very engaging and lectures are really fun. his exams are fair and you know what to expect, show up to class and study and you'll be fine

hes so funny and honeslty didnt really have to go to class but i went cause i liked him so much, also helps to go to class to get some extra info on top of hs slides. Makes u read the book but i did zero readings and got an 85 on both my midterms
Best class and teacher I've had so far, very funny and keeps things interesting!

C'était mon 2e cours avec professeur Bureau et j'ai adoré. Un des meilleurs prof que j'ai eu à l'université! Chaque cours est intérresant et tu peux clairement voir la passion et la connaissance du sujet lorsqu'il enseigne. Le projet est long mais il te guide tout au long. Je recommande a tous.

Bureau is an amazing prof. He prepares you well for midterms and exams. He asks his students to send him in questions then he brings them all together in one document. He picks his questions for MTs from that so you know what to expect. He talks about his daughters and is so funny. He's really passionate about what he teaches.
Un prof vraiment énergisant avec le materiel très claire. Des fois un peu trop facile, mais c'est facile de réussir à ces tests si tu complete les questions échantillons. Très charmant et gentil!

rComments: Un des meilleurs profs que j'ai eu a date! Il est tellement drole et rend les cours amusantes!
He is by far my favorite prof at the university! His lectures are really clear and he gives great examples to back up the theory!

Professor Bureau is a great prof. He is available to help and answer any questions you have. His labs are helpful to apply what you learn and are modern and fun. He is entertaining, encourages participation in class and communicates well the subject. The mid session project is a quite big, however, it is a unique and fun project to do.

Super comme prof. Il connait hyper bien la matière et il prend l'enseignement à coeur. J'ai adoré son cours! Super intéressant et stimulant. Les examens sont à choix multiples et il y a quelques questions à développement. Les questions à développement sont donnés en avance et il en choisi quelques unes parmi sa liste.
il y a des lectures, mais il parle de presque tout en classe. Il connaît très très bien la matière et il l'a rend intéressante avec des exemples vécues dans sa vie. Très bon prof.

Meilleur prof de psychologie que j'ai eu à date! Je le reprenderais à 100%. Il est important de prendre des notes lorsqu'il parle puisque ça l'aide. Il est clair des attentes pour les examens et donne toute les pistes à suivre. Les explications sont claires au point que je peux les comparer avec des choses que je vois dans ma vie quotidienne.
AMAZING. Enough said!!
Great Prof, he is passionate, funny and quirky. Easy A class if you study and do the textbook readings!

He delivers the lecture with humour and energy. Some of his examples are based on his personal life which makes it pretty easy to remember, especially when he acts it out (lol). His MCs can be tricky but overall, the exams are easy if you study! He's definitely one of the best profs I've ever had!

This prof is AMAZING. The best prof I have had so far. I'm always laughing in his classes. He is SO funny. I'm always looking forward to his classes like I'm literally excited to go to class. Isn't that great? Prof HIGHLY recommended.
Il est très drôle et ses cours son intéressant. Si tu vas à ses cours tu n'a pas besoin de faire les lectures.
Le meilleur prof que j'ai eu dans mes 4 ans à UOttawa. Il est passionné, et toujours à l'écoute des étudiants. Super.

Amazing prof. He is passionate, knowledgeable, sincere, and caring. He uses humor to get student students' attention, and then delivers the courses lectures. That just makes the course fun and instructive. Just great.
This prof is amazing. Loved his lectures. He gives really good examples to go with the theory. I actually looked forward to going to his classes.

One of the best profs I've had so far at uOttawa! Very knowledgeable of everything to do with child development and very passionate in his lectures. Tells hilarious stories and gives good examples to keep class interesting. I was always looking forward to these lectures.

Best prof I've ever had so far. Amazing lectures, and clearly knows what he is talking about. His classes are always very organised, and extremely interesting! He makes going to class something you WANT to do and not NEED to do. Would 100% take one of his classes again!! His midterms are very fair and gives you all the tools you need to pass :)
Bureau is such a good prof! He is super dynamic and his lectures are so interesting. He is super passionate about what he does and his exams are really easy!

Awesome prof!! Adore him! Il est tres gentil, drole at aprochable :) he is the bomb! Attendence is a good idea, he shows videos and explains content really well, makes it clear and alot easier to understand but he puts up pretty much all the notes and its all in the book. I didnt need to go but i wanted to!! Highly recommend
BEST TEACHER I EVER HAD
He's was a really good prof, super passionate and was pretty funny too. Make sure to do your reading though! Midterms (mc) are fair too.
He's super passionate about the topic and the lectures are amazing! I would recommend his classes for sure.

Jean-François Bureau est l'un des meilleurs professeurs que j'ai eu dans ma vie. Il est très drôle et donne le goût d'aller à ses cours. Il demande aux élèves d'envoyer des questions d'examen à développement court d'avance pour qu'on puisse bien se préparer. Les examens sont un peu dure, mais étudie et lis le manuel et tu vas réussir ! :)

Je suis à ma 4ième année d'université et il est définitivement un des meilleur prof que j'ai eu, sinon le meilleur. Rend la matière très intéressante et a pleins d'expériences personnelles à partager. Vraiment drôle et sympathique ; tout les profs devraient être comme lui. Je recommande n'importe quel de ses cours!
Great prof! Lectures were very enjoyable, his examples are very helpful!

Wow! Définitivement le meilleur prof de mon bacc. Super intéressant, passionné, motivé, à l'écoute de ses élèves. À recommander si vous cherchez un cours intéressant, auquel vous allez avoir hâte d'assister.

Le meilleur prof que j'ai eue en psycho à datte. Il est vraiment passionné et il capte ton attention super facilement. Son cours sur les enfants est plus qu'intéressant si vous les aimez ! Prenez ce cours il est malade !

On peut clariement voir qu'il aime enseigner et y est très bon. Peu importe qui tu es il saura capter ton attention avec son enthousiasme et son sens d'humour. Prenez son cour simplement pour l'avoir comme enseignant.

Ses cours sont très interessants.  Il est capable de garder ton attention pendant tout le cour, mais il dit souvent ''Ici au québec...'' les cours sont a Ottawa (ONTARIO) pas québec..  Très frustrant!
Excellent prof! You can tell he's passionate about the subject matter. Really helpful and open to questions. One of the best profs I've had
Excellent prof. Cours motivant. J'adore !
